  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_4' aria-label=\" Employer in Relation to Management of Katras Area of M/s Bharat Coking Coal Limited, Dhanbad versus Workman-Shahdeo Das pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('4','2025','2025_8_1481_1486','2025INSC1011'); ><font size='4'> <strong>EMPLOYER IN RELATION TO MANAGEMENT OF KATRAS AREA OF M/S BHARAT COKING COAL LIMITED, DHANBAD<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>WORKMAN-SHAHDEO DAS </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 8 S.C.R. 1481</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 1011</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010006502025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : VIKRAM NATH, SANDEEP MEHTA</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Issue arose as regards entertaining a claim for correction of date of birth in the service record after a delay of 25 years. Headnotes&dagger; Industrial dispute &ndash; Date of birth &ndash; Claim for correction of date of birth record after a delay of 25 years by the workman &ndash; Permissibility &ndash; Award by the Industrial Tribunal permitted the change in date of birth of the respondent- workman in the service record, after 25 years of joining service, from 1960 to 1972, based on a Transfer/School Leaving<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 13-08-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 2776/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('4','2025','2025_8_1481_1486','2025INSC1011','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='